{"tid":1069571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵相撞】事故頻仍年年加價   林鄭：難具體回應如何監督","createTime":"2019-03-20T05:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T14:13:31.000Z","uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e69a3d2d229a185592407a3bc4a0b44fdce3d697","tid":1069571,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:17:11.000Z","msg":"【港鐵相撞】事故頻仍年年加價 林鄭：難具體回應如何監督<br />\n1小時前1.4K<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n<br />\n港鐵荃灣綫日前在收車後測試新訊號系統，結果兩列列車在中環站隧道攔腰相撞至出軌，荃灣綫中環站至金鐘站要停駛兩日搶修，至今早始回復正常服務。有議員趁特首林鄭月娥到立法會出席答問環節時，批評港鐵接連爆出多宗醜聞，要求港府加強監督，並檢討現時的票價可加可減機制。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員陳恒鑌指，港鐵事故頻繁已令市民失去信心，而且港鐵每年大賺幾百億之餘，仍年年加價，要求港府加強監督港鐵，並趁港鐵管理層換屆提早檢討可加可減機制。"},{"pid":"5c25d4f894eb2dac2f20339e45a90aa99bd562cc","tid":1069571,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"林鄭回應時先感謝港鐵前線人員及消防署協助清理事故的辛勞，<span style=\"color: red;\">她指自己和身兼港鐵董事局成員的特區官員都關心港鐵的問題，會「加把勁」監督，但現時難以具體回應如何協助及加強監督</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。至於可否提前檢討可加可減機制，她僅表示已聽到有關意見。<br />\n<br />\n議員謝偉銓再追問會否改革監督港鐵的制度，林鄭就稱每個機構都會出現問題，不相信會有機構歷久不衰，因此要時常反省，歡迎議員提意見改善公營機構的管理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190320/59389195?fbclid=IwAR1q2adyM_PbGYimWXEakKFB99X_Y0FyQkM0SkWcFSFvmrWzTqNUsQ39lDw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59389195%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1q2adyM_PbGYimWXEakKFB99X_Y0FyQkM0SkWcFSFvmrWzTqNUsQ39lDw&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9G9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=e972aaf2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190320%2F59389195%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1q2adyM_PbGYimWXEakKFB99X_Y0FyQkM0SkWcFSFvmrWzTqNUsQ39lDw&h=36a30f41\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190320/59389195?fbclid=IwAR1q2adyM_PbGYimWXEakKFB99X_Y0FyQkM0SkWcFSFvmrWzTqNUsQ39lDw</a>"},{"pid":"defa131f2696d2be76004ef55ac62f924491eca5","tid":1069571,"uid":95138,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"啫係冇監督<br />\n機電署鐵路科廢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b33c398866872abda1f0adcc093397f24fd8ab9","tid":1069571,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:21:22.000Z","msg":"咁要你做特首做乜柒<br />\n幫雜種奶屎眼就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda26583e2f509ef1f50868491dc2e0dd83ae1a1","tid":1069571,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b33c398866872abda1f0adcc093397f24fd8ab9","tid":1069571,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:21:22.000Z","msg":"咁要你做特首做乜柒<br />\n幫雜種奶屎眼就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:26:50.000Z","msg":"白逗人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbb59d126c1b469a2d70632834c182f22de5600","tid":1069571,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:50:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c800d1f07ea74eb47020b06e2ef99bee35572ca","tid":1069571,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"咁要政府做咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3b39708cff420031e09042963fd6138f798980","tid":1069571,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c800d1f07ea74eb47020b06e2ef99bee35572ca","tid":1069571,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"咁要政府做咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"忙緊同大灣區接軌<br />\n哩d野唔得閒搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dc61ea4234a13